mco.account.privacy.info: Read thou the Mojang informations and privacy laws
mco.account.privacyinfo:
Mojang, by their proceedings to vouchsafe children their privacy, does comply with the Children’s On-line Privacy Protection Act (COPPA) and General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). 
 
If thou art a youngling you require leave and permission of thy parents to access the Realms.
 
Shouldst ye possess a foregone Minecraft account form (ye log in with thy name only), and thou'ldst access Realms, you must migrate thine account to Mojang.
